Description: DoodleMe — AI-assisted robot design rqt plugin
 Conversational interface for designing 3D printed mechanical and
 electronics robot assemblies. Powered by Claude LLM; generates
 OpenSCAD, URDF, Bill of Materials, wiring diagrams, and KiCad
 schematics with live RViz2 preview and Gazebo simulation support.
